properties.name: spring.aop.proxy-target-class
properties.description: Whether subclass-based (CGLIB) proxies are to be created (true) as opposed to standard Java interface-based proxies (false).

properties.name: spring.batch.enabled
properties.description: Execute all Spring Batch jobs in the context on startup.

properties.name: spring.datasource.jmx-enabled
properties.description: Enables JMX support (if provided by the underlying pool).

properties.name: spring.jmx.enabled
properties.description: Automatically expose management beans to the JMX domain

properties.name: spring.jpa.open-in-view
properties.description: Automatically register OpenEntityManagerInViewInterceptor. Binds a JPA EntityManager to the thread for the entire processing of the request.

properties.name: spring.social.auto-connection-views
properties.description: Automatically enable the connection status view for supported providers.
